metadata.name: Ancient Alien #1
metadata.description: In a galaxy far, far away, named The Nifty Way, an advanced Alien civilization, The Nifties, have been watching us for thousands of years. They’ve become huge fans of the human race since they started intercepting all of our music, tv, movies, games and everything related to our culture. From then on, they’ve been trying their best to dress and behave like us, making sure we will like them when it's time to finally meet them. Now, they’re ready to meet us.
